Title: Series: Schola Italica Picturae
Description: Rest on the flight into Egypt, after Barocci; the Virgin dips a bowl into a pool of water as Joseph and Jesus play with a tree branch with berries; the donkey stands at right. 1772 Etching and engraving
Curator's comments: See 1856,0510.229 for comment on series. After a painting by Barocci known through several versions, see A. Emiliani, 'Federico Barocci', 1985, volume I, pages 78-85.
